          >
            <div
              class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start w-full space-y-8 xl:space-y-16"
            >
              <Icon
                as="div"
                name="paint"
                className="h-10 w-10 xl:h-12 xl:w-12 text-blue-600 animate-wiggle mr-8"
              />
              <h2 class="2xl:text-4xl xl:text-3xl text-2xl">Creative</h2>

              <ul
                class="list-disc text-zinc-400 grid lg:grid-cols-1 gap-x-10 gap-y-2 px-4 pt-4 2xl:text-xl md:text-lg text-md"
              >
                <li>HCP, Patient, and Consumer Content Development</li>
                <li>Regulatory-Compliant Creative (PAAB & ASC Expertise)</li>
                <li>Sales Enablement Tools and Marketing Collateral</li>
                <li>Booth and Exhibit Design</li>
                <li>Corporate Communications and Messaging</li>
                <li>Logo and Visual Identity Development</li>
                <li>Brand Guidelines and Style Guide Creation</li>
                <li>
                  Commercial Print Services (Conference, Sales and Marketing
                  Materials)
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="2xl:p-24 p-8 md:p-16 border border-zinc-800 w-full flex flex-col justify-start items-center mb-8"
          >
            <div
              class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start w-full space-y-8 xl:space-y-16"
            >
              <div>
                <Icon
                  as="div"
                  name="chevronRight"
                  className="h-10 w-10 xl:h-12 xl:w-12 text-violet-700 animate-wiggle"
